import React from 'react'
import Hero from '../main/Hero'
import DreamTeam from '../main/DreamTeam'
import FarGalaxy from '../main/FarGalaxy'

  return (
    <main className="clearfix">
      <Hero />
      <DreamTeam />
      <FarGalaxy />
    </main>
  )
}

export default Home
